name: RM Padang Muaro Painan
address: Jl. Raya Denpasar - Gilimanuk, Baler Bale Agung, Kec. Negara, Kabupaten Jembrana, Bali 82218, Indonesia
review 1:
Good food, cheap prices, & fast, friendly service. Conveniently located with car parking available.
Stopped here again (5th time) & food was wonderful! Many vegetarian options & not too spicy, unless you add sambel (which I highly recommend!) They also have fish, chicken and beef options. The beef rendang is so tender & flavorful!
review 2:
Delicious padang food. Nice service. Simple place. 2 persons ordered fried chicken, limpa, kikil, fried fish, blanched tapioca, sayur nangka, sambal ijo, 2 rice n 2 ice tea for only Rp. 90,000
Will come back again if ever in Bali.
review 3: Ok padang food n service, half-done constructed building with permanently closed glass windows so hot..
review 4: The best Padang food in Jembrana. Big portion (especially for takeaway). Highly reccommend
